WEBVTT

00:02.100 --> 00:03.260
- I HAVE A KID.

00:03.310 --> 00:04.754
HIS NAME IS JABBAR.

00:04.790 --> 00:05.859
- HEY, DID YOU TAKE THE TEST?

00:05.900 --> 00:07.447
- THE TEST?
- THE PATERNITY TEST.

00:07.490 --> 00:09.242
- I WANT TO GET
A PATERNITY TEST.

00:09.280 --> 00:11.168
- UM, I'M MARK CYR,
11TH-GRADE ENGLISH.

00:11.210 --> 00:12.416
- MY DAUGHTER'S TEACHER.

00:12.460 --> 00:14.143
YOU KNOW WHAT?
I'M TRYING TO IMPRESS YOU.

00:14.180 --> 00:15.659
- I-I-IT WORKED.
[chuckles]

00:15.700 --> 00:17.315
- YOU MUST BE JULIA.
- THIS IS RACQUEL.

00:17.360 --> 00:19.146
- HI.
- YOU ARE SO AMAZING.

00:19.190 --> 00:19.975
- OH.
- MWAH.

00:20.020 --> 00:22.079
- ALL RIGHTY.

00:23.920 --> 00:27.083
[Adam and Kristina moaning]

00:30.090 --> 00:33.924
- OH.
- HONEY, WOW.

00:33.960 --> 00:35.268
- OH.

00:35.310 --> 00:37.266
[sighs]

00:37.310 --> 00:40.165
- WHEW.

00:40.210 --> 00:43.179
HONEY, I HAVE TO WASH
MAX'S BANDANA.

00:43.210 --> 00:44.313
- HUH?
- IT'S FILTHY.

00:44.350 --> 00:45.556
IF HE'S GONNA BE A PIRATE,

00:45.590 --> 00:47.171
AT LEAST HE'S GONNA BE
A CLEAN PIRATE.

00:47.210 --> 00:48.723
IT'S LIKE RING
AROUND THE NECK.

00:48.770 --> 00:50.385
OH, MY GOD, AND HIS
BEHAVIORAL AIDE IS GONNA BE HERE

00:50.420 --> 00:52.047
AT 10:00,
AND WE BOTH NEED

00:52.080 --> 00:53.490
TO BE ON THE SAME PAGE
WITH ALL THIS STUFF.

00:53.530 --> 00:55.179
I HAVE A THOUSAND QUESTIONS
THAT I WANT TO ASK HER,

00:55.220 --> 00:56.323
AND YOU KNOW WHAT ELSE?

00:56.360 --> 00:58.601
