THEN, WERE YOU?

25:30.870 --> 25:33.077
- NO. I SWEAR.
- YOU SURE?

25:33.110 --> 25:34.793
- YEAH.
YEAH.

25:37.120 --> 25:38.838
- I JUST--YOU KNOW,
I WANT TO BE ABLE TO KNOW

25:38.880 --> 25:42.873
