30:17.220 --> 30:18.289
- NO REASON.

30:18.330 --> 30:19.228
- OH, NO, NO.

30:19.260 --> 30:21.364
- ALL RIGHT,
I'M OUT OF HERE.

30:21.400 --> 30:23.504
- UNLESS--NO, NO, WAIT.
