TO FEEL BAD.

30:40.180 --> 30:42.410
- GOD, THIS IS JUST HORRIBLE.
- IT'S NOT HORRIBLE.

30:42.460 --> 30:43.722
- WHAT, ARE YOU ALL IN ON THIS?
