- YES.

31:14.280 --> 31:15.588
- HOW--HOW IS FAKING IT
A GIFT?

31:15.630 --> 31:17.313
- BECAUSE IT SAYS TO YOU,

31:17.350 --> 31:19.409
"THANK YOU SO MUCH FOR TRYING.

31:19.460 --> 31:21.212
"PLEASE COME AGAIN SOON.

31:21.250 --> 31:22.877
