LIGHTBULBS...

31:27.710 --> 31:28.870
- SO COME BACK AGAIN
NEXT TIME,

31:28.920 --> 31:31.127
AND I'LL JUST GIVE
HIM THOSE. OKAY.

31:31.160 --> 31:33.082
